Agent Operating Procedures (AOPs)

No more rigid systems that require slow and costly professional services to build and maintain. Use natural language instructions that compile into code to dynamically handle complex, real-world situations.

Learn more

The best of both

AOPs combine the power and flexibility of natural language instructions with the precision and rigor of code to reliably scale AI agents.

Natural language instructions

CX operators quickly architect and iterate on AI logic, similar to how they’d teach humans Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs).

Control over core code

Technical teams retain control over guardrail enforcement and connections with internal systems to pull data or take action.

True omnichannel support

Decagon provides one centralized AI engine to auto-resolve issues at any time, in every language, and across every channel. Say goodbye to stitched-together point solutions with siloed and disjointed logic.
